title: The Choice For A New Generation | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: The Choice For A New Generation | Joel Osteen
description:
The decisions we make don’t just affect us, they affect our future generations. Make up your mind to put an end to the negative strongholds in your family line. God wants to help you leave a legacy of favor for your family.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
